ᠤᠯᠭ᠎ᠠ ᠪᠢᠰᠢ ᠶᠤᠮ᠃ ᠭᠤᠷᠪᠠᠳᠤᠭᠠᠷ ᠲᠤ᠂ ᠪᠦᠬᠦ ᠵᠢᠭᠰᠠᠭᠴᠢᠳ ᠢ ᠰᠤᠯᠠᠯᠠ᠃ ᠳᠥᠷᠪᠡᠳᠦᠭᠡᠷ ᠲᠦ᠂ ᠴᠠᠭᠳᠠᠭ᠎ᠠ ᠨᠠᠷ ᠢ ᠮᠥᠷᠳᠡᠨ ᠰᠢᠯᠭᠠᠬᠤ᠃ ᠡᠴᠦᠰ ᠲᠦ ᠨᠢ᠂ ᠺᠠᠷᠷᠢ ᠵᠠᠶᠢᠯᠠᠭᠤᠯᠬᠤ ᠱᠠᠭᠠᠷᠳᠠᠯᠭ᠎ᠠ ᠲᠠᠢ ᠪᠠᠶᠢᠨ᠎ᠠ᠃"},{"pid":"18d87293fa4b5b07fcfa0906e37fd2f3a08c3258","tid":1297151,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"ᠬᠡᠷᠪᠡ ᠲᠠ ᠡᠨᠡ ᠬᠡᠯᠡ ᠶᠢ ᠣᠷᠴᠢᠭᠤᠯᠬᠤ ᠪᠣᠯᠤᠮᠵᠢ ᠲᠠᠢ ᠪᠣᠯ ᠲᠠ ᠤᠬᠠᠭᠠᠯᠢᠭ ᠪᠠᠶᠢᠨ᠎ᠠ<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Aeropuerto_de_Hong_Kong%2C_2013-08-13%2C_DD_02.JPG/1280px-Aeropuerto_de_Hong_Kong%2C_2013-08-13%2C_DD_02.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F28%2FAeropuerto_de_Hong_Kong%252C_2013-08-13%252C_DD_02.JPG%2F1280px-Aeropuerto_de_Hong_Kong%252C_2013-08-13%252C_DD_02.JPG&h=36d3cc17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nᠪᠢ 6 ᠴᠠᠭ ᠲᠤ ᠣᠷᠣᠢ ᠶᠢᠨ ᠬᠣᠭᠣᠯᠠ ᠢᠳᠡᠮᠡᠷ ᠰᠠᠨᠠᠭᠳᠠᠳᠠᠭ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nᠬᠦᠨᠡᠰᠦ᠄ ᠲᠥᠮᠥᠰᠥ<br />\nᠴᠠᠭ ᠬᠤᠭᠤᠴᠠᠭ᠎ᠠ᠄ 1800-2000<br />\nᠪᠠᠭᠠᠵᠢ ᠬᠡᠷᠡᠭᠰᠡᠯ᠄ ᠰᠡᠷᠡᠭᠡ᠂ ᠬᠠᠯᠪᠠᠭ᠎ᠠ<br />\nᠲᠠᠨ ᠢ ᠷᠧᠰᠲ᠋ᠣᠷᠠᠨ ᠳᠤ ᠦᠵᠡᠭᠡᠷᠡᠢ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd1a0e09dea7b0f292221ab99f1dd4b9bdcb298","tid":1297151,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"ᠬᠡᠨ ᠴᠤ ᠡᠭᠦᠨ ᠢ ᠬᠡᠷᠬᠢᠨ ᠣᠷᠴᠢᠭᠤᠯᠬᠤ ᠪᠠᠨ ᠮᠡᠳᠡᠬᠦ ᠦᠭᠡᠢ ᠪᠠᠶᠢᠨ᠎ᠠ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59976bbdbd8c47629c27ad460032829b99bcd320","tid":1297151,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"無人識對表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd5def52aab9d6eacea30c3ebd2bf7219fe5019","tid":129715