:"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e455f845d94e5c4c2268b8fe1b17cf12f6a44b8","tid":1297151,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:04:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，拉籠一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派五毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持頭腦清晰，和理非同勇武都係一齊合作嘅同伴，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易中咗政府同三毛嘅分化計<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次唔排除有三毛混入開假膠post / 推膠post，之前嗰啲垃圾post我當一時on9，如果今日起（9/7/2019）再發現有任何人開膠post，一律當三毛處理</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ed5a3afc2b927f575f4c7304ddcbd4a8e3b29fe","tid":1297151,"uid":108512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"ea76cc43ab0a97d4fa2f2cd4aab12d6231c8b052","tid":1297151,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主如果你唔想單機，勸你即刻收手兼道歉</span></span>"},{"pid":"0b6df31e8ee20e031cfe7027a2a9a94b97f6c67f","tid":1297151,"uid":120400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eeb76b61cf143261f4ab56f3a9c9bc6406115924","tid":1297151,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你冇做錯到"},{"pid":"67a88f5b0dd9cc0ddcc7d6987edaa005eac41d76","tid":1297151,"uid":49936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>咪撚再玩，今晚係無任何活動<br />\n亂碼係製造假象</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"914c45f